name: Hello My Name Is Revenge
description: It's a long story how I got the name. Get my human drunk and he might tell you how he saved me from the Sunday school kids and gave me that name. This is my very first NFT and is the beginning of my quest to be famous. Or at least the most famous NFT dinosaur around:) I'm going to mint a bunch of these and make them cheap so everyone can have something to look at and make them smile. From here on out though it's going to be editions of 5 and still pretty cheap. I want you to fight over me;)
